The blog [Guatemala Solidarity
Network](http://www.guatemalasolidarity.org.uk/node/322) and James Rodriguez
from [Mi Mundo](http://www.mimundo.org/2012/06/14/2012-06-guatemalan-female-
activist-shot-for-leading-blockade-against-a-canadian-owned-gold-mine/) report
on the attempted murder of anti-mining activist Yolanda “Yoli” Oquely Veliz.
The [Guatemala Human Rights Commission/USA
](http://salsa.democracyinaction.org/o/2690/p/dia/action/public/?action_KEY=10817)condemns
the shooting and invites citizens to sign a petition “to call on the
Guatemalan Government to investigate this crime and prosecute those
responsible.”

